"```typescript\n"
"canvas.setFillColor(1.0, 0.0, 0.0, 1.0)    // red\n"
"canvas.fillRect(10, 10, 100, 80)\n"
"\n"
"canvas.setStrokeColor(0.0, 0.0, 1.0, 1.0)  // blue\n"
"canvas.setLineWidth(2)\n"
"canvas.strokeRect(150, 10, 100, 80)\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/ui/canvas.md:40
