#: src/ui/tray.md:3
msgid ""
"Perry ships a cross-platform system tray API on `perry/ui` (issue #490). The"
" same six functions work on every desktop target — macOS, Windows, "
"Linux/GTK4 — and link as no-ops on the mobile / embedded backends."
msgstr ""
"Perry include un'API di system tray cross-platform su `perry/ui` (issue "
"#490). Le stesse sei funzioni funzionano su ogni target desktop — macOS, "
"Windows, Linux/GTK4 — e si collegano come no-op sui backend mobile / "
"embedded."

#: src/ui/tray.md:7
msgid ""
"The API is **handle-based** and free-function: build a tray with "
"`trayCreate(iconPath)`, attach a context menu built with the existing "
"`menuCreate` / `menuAddItem` API via `trayAttachMenu(tray, menu)`, and "
"register a left-click callback with `trayOnClick`."
msgstr ""
"L'API è **basata su handle** e a funzioni libere: creare un tray con "
"`trayCreate(iconPath)`, collegare un menu contestuale costruito con l'API "
"esistente `menuCreate` / `menuAddItem` tramite `trayAttachMenu(tray, menu)`,"
" e registrare una callback al clic sinistro con `trayOnClick`."

#: src/ui/tray.md:14
msgid ""
"```typescript\n"
"// Build the tray BEFORE App() — the tray icon installs while the\n"
"// runtime is starting up, so it's already live when the main window\n"
"// appears.\n"
"const tray = trayCreate(\"\")  // empty path → \"●\" placeholder\n"
"traySetTooltip(tray, \"My App\")\n"
"\n"
"// Right-click (or left-click on macOS) opens the menu attached below.\n"
"const menu = menuCreate()\n"
"menuAddItem(menu, \"Show\", () => status.set(\"tray/show\"))\n"
"menuAddSeparator(menu)\n"
"menuAddItem(menu, \"Quit\", () => status.set(\"tray/quit\"))\n"
"trayAttachMenu(tray, menu)\n"
"\n"
"// Optional: left-click handler. On macOS the menu pops on left-click,\n"
"// so this fires only when no menu is attached. On Windows / Linux,\n"
"// left-click and the menu are independent — typical usage is\n"
"// \"left-click → show main window, right-click → menu\".\n"
"trayOnClick(tray, () => {\n"
"    status.set(\"tray/click\")\n"
"})\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/ui/tray.md:37 src/ui/webview.md:168 src/platforms/windows-7.md:23
#: src/container/overview.md:69 src/system/background.md:24
#: src/plugins/appstore-review.md:54
msgid "API"
msgstr "API"

#: src/ui/tray.md:41
msgid "`trayCreate(iconPath: string): Widget`"
msgstr "`trayCreate(iconPath: string): Widget`"

#: src/ui/tray.md:41
msgid ""
"Create the tray icon. `iconPath` is a filesystem path to a PNG (or `.icns` "
"on macOS, `.ico` on Windows). Pass `\"\"` to use a \"●\" placeholder."
msgstr ""
"Crea l'icona nella tray. `iconPath` è un percorso del filesystem verso un "
"file PNG (oppure `.icns` su macOS, `.ico` su Windows). Passa `\"\"` per "
"usare un segnaposto \"●\"."

#: src/ui/tray.md:42
msgid "`traySetIcon(tray, iconPath)`"
msgstr "`traySetIcon(tray, iconPath)`"

#: src/ui/tray.md:42
msgid "Hot-swap the icon image. Empty path is a no-op."
msgstr ""
"Sostituisce l'immagine dell'icona a caldo. Un percorso vuoto è un no-op."

#: src/ui/tray.md:43
msgid "`traySetTooltip(tray, tooltip)`"
msgstr "`traySetTooltip(tray, tooltip)`"

#: src/ui/tray.md:43
msgid "Set the tooltip text shown on hover."
msgstr "Imposta il testo del tooltip mostrato al passaggio del mouse."

#: src/ui/tray.md:44
msgid "`trayAttachMenu(tray, menu)`"
msgstr "`trayAttachMenu(tray, menu)`"

#: src/ui/tray.md:44
msgid ""
"Attach a context menu (built with `menuCreate` / `menuAddItem`). Right-click"
" — or left-click on macOS — opens the menu."
msgstr ""
"Collega un menu contestuale (costruito con `menuCreate` / `menuAddItem`). Il"
" clic destro — o il clic sinistro su macOS — apre il menu."

#: src/ui/tray.md:45
msgid "`trayOnClick(tray, callback)`"
msgstr "`trayOnClick(tray, callback)`"

#: src/ui/tray.md:45
msgid ""
"Register a left-click handler. On macOS the menu pops on left-click, so this"
" only fires when no menu is attached; on Windows / Linux, left-click and "
"menu are independent."
msgstr ""
"Registra un handler per il clic sinistro. Su macOS il menu si apre al clic "
"sinistro, quindi questo si attiva solo quando non è collegato nessun menu; "
"su Windows / Linux, il clic sinistro e il menu sono indipendenti."

#: src/ui/tray.md:46
msgid "`trayDestroy(tray)`"
msgstr "`trayDestroy(tray)`"

#: src/ui/tray.md:46
msgid ""
"Remove the icon. The handle stays valid (subsequent setters are no-ops) so "
"existing closures don't crash."
msgstr ""
"Rimuove l'icona. L'handle rimane valido (le successive chiamate ai setter "
"diventano no-op) in modo che le closure esistenti non vadano in crash."

#: src/ui/tray.md:48
msgid "Updating the Icon"
msgstr "Aggiornare l'icona"

#: src/ui/tray.md:50
msgid ""
"```typescript\n"
"// Hot-swap the icon. The path can be a PNG (every platform), .icns\n"
"// (macOS), or .ico (Windows). Empty path is a no-op.\n"
"traySetIcon(tray, \"./assets/tray.png\")\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

#: src/ui/tray.md:56
msgid "Removal"
msgstr "Rimozione"

#: src/ui/tray.md:58
msgid ""
"```typescript\n"
"// Remove the tray icon. After this, the handle is dead — set_icon /\n"
"// set_tooltip / attach_menu calls become no-ops.\n"
"trayDestroy(tray)\n"
"```"
msgstr ""

