#: src/platforms/tvos.md:53
msgid "Focus-based navigation"
msgstr "Navigazione basata sul focus"

#: src/platforms/tvos.md:54
msgid "On-screen keyboard via Siri Remote"
msgstr "Tastiera su schermo tramite Siri Remote"

