" watchos-widget`. The same `Widget({...})` source produces both iOS and "
"watchOS widgets — the supported families determine the rendering."
msgstr ""
"I widget Perry possono compilare verso complicazioni WidgetKit di watchOS "
"usando `--target watchos-widget`. La stessa sorgente `Widget({...})` produce"
" sia widget iOS che watchOS — le famiglie supportate determinano il "
"rendering."

#: src/widgets/watchos.md:5
msgid ""
"**Status:** the snippet on this page compile-links cleanly on the host LLVM "
"target via "
"[`docs/examples/widgets/snippets.ts`](https://github.com/PerryTS/perry/blob/main/docs/examples/widgets/snippets.ts),"
" so the `Widget({...})` shape is verified against the codegen. The actual "
"`--target watchos-widget` / `--target watchos-widget-simulator` cross-"
"compile is wired in `crates/perry/src/commands/compile.rs` (emits through "
"the WidgetKit Swift emitter) but the doc-tests harness can't drive it yet — "
"each cross-target requires `--app-bundle-id` not yet surfaced through the "
"harness ([\\#194](https://github.com/PerryTS/perry/issues/194)) plus a "
"watchOS SDK from Xcode. Build with the `perry` CLI to validate end-to-end."
msgstr ""
"**Stato:** il frammento in questa pagina si compila e linka correttamente "
"sul target LLVM host tramite "
"[`docs/examples/widgets/snippets.ts`](https://github.com/PerryTS/perry/blob/main/docs/examples/widgets/snippets.ts),"
" quindi la forma `Widget({...})` è verificata rispetto al codegen. Il cross-"
"compile con `--target watchos-widget` / `--target watchos-widget-simulator` "
"è collegato in `crates/perry/src/commands/compile.rs` (emette tramite "
"l'emitter Swift WidgetKit) ma il harness di doc-test non riesce ancora a "
"gestirlo — ogni cross-target richiede `--app-bundle-id` non ancora esposto "
"tramite il harness ([\\#194](https://github.com/PerryTS/perry/issues/194)) "
"oltre a un SDK watchOS da Xcode. Compilare con la CLI `perry` per validare "
"end-to-end."

