#: src/cli/commands.md:285
msgid ""
"`perry setup windows` downloads the Microsoft CRT + Windows SDK libraries "
"(~1.5 GB) so Perry can link without Visual Studio Build Tools. Requires LLVM"
" (`winget install LLVM.LLVM`) and prompts to accept the Microsoft "
"redistributable license — pass `--accept-license` to skip the prompt for CI."
" Output lands at `%LOCALAPPDATA%\\perry\\windows-sdk`. See the [Windows "
"platform guide](../platforms/windows.md) for the full toolchain comparison."
msgstr ""
"`perry setup windows` scarica le librerie Microsoft CRT + Windows SDK (~1,5 "
"GB) in modo che Perry possa collegare senza Visual Studio Build Tools. "
"Richiede LLVM (`winget install LLVM.LLVM`) e chiede di accettare la licenza "
"ridistribuibile Microsoft — passa `--accept-license` per saltare il prompt "
"in CI. L'output viene salvato in `%LOCALAPPDATA%\\perry\\windows-sdk`. "
"Consulta la [guida alla piattaforma Windows](../platforms/windows.md) per il"
" confronto completo della toolchain."

