#: src/contributing/architecture.md:58
msgid ""
"Generational mark-sweep GC, per-thread arena split into nursery + old-gen. "
"Roots come from a precise shadow stack (emitted by codegen), a conservative "
"native-stack scan, and 9 registered runtime scanners. Two-bit aging tenures "
"objects after surviving 2 minor cycles; a write barrier maintains a "
"remembered set for old → young pointers."
msgstr ""
"GC mark-sweep generazionale, arena per-thread divisa in nursery + old-gen. "
"Le radici provengono da uno shadow stack preciso (emesso dal codegen), una "
"scansione conservativa dello stack nativo e 9 scanner runtime registrati. "
"L'aging a due bit promuove gli oggetti dopo aver superato 2 cicli minori; "
"una write barrier mantiene un remembered set per i puntatori da old a young."

